{
  "texts": [
    "Icarus Verilog is then used to evaluate the generated SystemVerilog against the reference solution.",
    "Lastly, a failure classification script detects keywords in the Icarus Verilog output (both compile time and runtime) to classify failures.",
    "A summary of failures across problems is saved into a text file for human analysis.",
    "Specification-to-RTL DatasetTest Benches Golden References ICL Prompts ProbXXX/ Working Directory Code Completion Dataset sampleYY-sv-generation.log sample-YY-sv-iv-test.log ProbXXX-sampleYY.sv Test Benches Golden References ICL Prompts Makefile Icarus Verilog sv-generate Python Script LLM Under Test Failure Classification Python Script summary.txt Each dataset consists of the associated prompts and in-context learning examples for the given task category.",
    "The Makefile runs Python scripts and Icarus Verilog to prompt the LLM with the given problems and ICL examples, captures and simulates the responses, and classifies failures."
